data.title: The Bulldog Newsletter
data.text:
USCGC ALEX HALEY (WMEC 39)

"The Bulldog of the Bering"

THE BULLDOG NEWSLETTER

On February 8th, 2014 our Public Affairs staff released the first edition of what would become one of the most popular cutter newsletters in the fleet. "The Bulldog", coined after USCGC ALEX HALEY's nickname, is a monthly newsletter that finds its way to our friends and families around the country, informing them of cutter operations and shipboard activities. Please find available below our past newsletters.
